525
00:48:08,710 --> 00:48:15,100
She saw a face. He walked among the tourists
at the hotel's front desk. He was trying to

526
00:48:15,100 --> 00:48:21,810
look as though he belonged here, but his eyes
were searching. The face was long and thin,

527
00:48:21,810 --> 00:48:26,440
and he wore round glasses. He was a little
