528
00:48:26,440 --> 00:48:34,089
'Gavin, listen to me,' she said. 'I have to
go. I can see a man I've seen before, about

529
00:48:34,089 --> 00:48:35,240
an hour ago.'

530
00:48:35,240 --> 00:48:39,480
'OK. Take care, Darby, and call me again soon.'

531
00:48:39,480 --> 00:48:45,359
'I'll try.'

532
00:48:45,359 --> 00:48:50,829
CHAPTER EIGHT
Photos and Phone Calls

