00:49:03,619 --> 00:49:11,369
of the car. With his powerful camera he could
almost read the names in the phone book. A

536
00:49:11,369 --> 00:49:13,730
large woman was using the phone at the moment.

537
00:49:13,730 --> 00:49:21,250
At 12:20 the woman put the phone down and
walked away. From nowhere a young man in a

538
00:49:21,250 --> 00:49:29,040
suit appeared and walked over to the phone.
Croft felt sure that this was the man. He

539
00:49:29,040 --> 00:49:34,200
picked up his camera and looked through it.
The man was pushing numbers on the phone and

540
00:49:34,200 --> 00:49:42,250
looked nervous. He kept looking this way and
that. Croft took a couple of pictures.

541
00:49:42,250 --> 00:49:48,960
The phone in the car went three times. Croft
didn't pick it up. It was Grantham at the

