546
00:50:18,080 --> 00:50:19,080
***

547
00:50:19,080 --> 00:50:23,809
Grantham got plenty of excellent pictures
from Croft. Garcia didn't look Spanish, despite

548
00:50:23,809 --> 00:50:30,940
the name he had chosen. He looked like thousands
of other young lawyers up and down the country.

549
00:50:30,940 --> 00:50:37,470
From Garcia he got nothing. It didn't matter.
He let him talk about his wife and child,

550
00:50:37,470 --> 00:50:45,460
and how frightened he was. One day, and one
day soon, Garcia would give him the information,

551
00:50:45,460 --> 00:50:48,079
whatever it was.

552
00:50:48,079 --> 00:50:53,890
From Sarge he got a copy of a White House
document naming Khamel as the probable killer

553
00:50:53,890 --> 00:51:00,491
of Rosenberg and Jensen. This was good. There
