556
00:51:15,430 --> 00:51:16,430
***

557
00:51:16,430 --> 00:51:21,039
The phone was going. After twenty-four hours
on the run, she had drunk a bottle of wine

558
00:51:21,039 --> 00:51:27,859
the night before and fallen asleep on her
bed in the Marriott Hotel. But first she had

559
00:51:27,859 --> 00:51:34,040
cut off her long red hair and coloured it
black; they would be expecting blonde. They

560
00:51:34,040 --> 00:51:40,609
would also be expecting her to run away, so
despite her fears she stayed in New Orleans.

561
00:51:40,609 --> 00:51:47,050
They would be watching all the police stations,
so she had stayed away from them.

562
00:51:47,050 --> 00:51:54,869
The phone was still going. She picked it up
and heard 'Darby? This is Gavin.'

563
00:51:54,869 --> 00:51:58,560
Now she was awake. 'How did you find me?'

564
00:51:58,560 --> 00:52:02,619
'We are the FBI. We have our ways.'

565
00:52:02,619 --> 00:52:10,940
'Wait. Let me think. Of course, you can trace
me when I use my cards to pay for things.

566
00:52:10,940 --> 00:52:17,521
How stupid of me! But if you can find me,
they can find me too. They could be outside

567
00:52:17,521 --> 00:52:19,660
the door now.'

568
00:52:19,660 --> 00:52:28,470
'Stay in small hotels, then, and pay with
