578
00:53:04,990 --> 00:53:06,250
'Yes.'

579
00:53:06,250 --> 00:53:13,150
'Thanks. If Thomas was murdered because of
the brief, then we know who killed him. And

580
00:53:13,150 --> 00:53:19,960
if we know who killed Thomas, then we know
who killed Rosenberg and Jensen. Am I right?'

581
00:53:19,960 --> 00:53:20,960
'Probably.'

582
00:53:20,960 --> 00:53:28,420
'That's good enough - "probably" means "yes"
