583
00:53:28,420 --> 00:53:30,910
doing nothing about my suspect.'

584
00:53:30,910 --> 00:53:39,079
'Calm down, Darby. Let's meet tonight and
talk about this. I could save your life.'

585
00:53:39,079 --> 00:53:43,650
She carefully put the receiver of the phone
under the pillow. She threw her things into

586
00:53:43,650 --> 00:53:49,780
a bag and left the room. She walked up two
floors to the seventeenth, then took the lift

587
00:53:49,780 --> 00:53:56,340
down to the tenth. Then she walked down the
stairs to the ground floor. She hid in the

588
00:53:56,340 --> 00:54:00,200
women's room for half an hour, and then left
