00:54:07,010 --> 00:54:10,180
back. She called Verheek.

591
00:54:10,180 --> 00:54:15,289
'Where will you stay tonight?' she asked him.

592
00:54:15,289 --> 00:54:17,470
'At the Hilton.'

593
00:54:17,470 --> 00:54:21,940
'I'll call late tonight or early in the morning.'

594
00:54:21,940 --> 00:54:25,800
'Can you get the Washington Post down there?
