595
00:54:25,800 --> 00:54:31,910
'I can't wait. I'll speak to you later.'

596
00:54:31,910 --> 00:54:38,420
She bought a Post and read it at another cafe.
If the report was right, it fitted in with

597
00:54:38,420 --> 00:54:44,950
her theory. The local paper had a picture
