598
00:54:44,950 --> 00:54:51,380
story about the explosion. The police were
looking for a white female whom several witnesses

599
00:54:51,380 --> 00:55:00,440
had seen there at the time. She looked slowly
at the photo of Thomas. He was so handsome.

600
00:55:00,440 --> 00:55:02,589
Tears filled her eyes.

601
00:55:02,589 --> 00:55:03,589
***

602
00:55:03,589 --> 00:55:09,720
Alice Stark, Darby's best friend, got the
