949
01:25:34,230 --> 01:25:40,670
but there was no Garcia. He was sure of it.

950
01:25:40,670 --> 01:25:41,670
***

951
01:25:41,670 --> 01:25:47,179
Some of the people employed by the White House
didn't work at the White House; some were

952
01:25:47,179 --> 01:25:53,510
so secret that their offices were elsewhere
