953
01:25:53,510 --> 01:25:58,400
Matthew Barr was one of these shadowy people.

954
01:25:58,400 --> 01:26:03,690
He was riding in the back of the car with
Coal. Coal was silent while Barr read the

955
01:26:03,690 --> 01:26:12,040
Pelican Brief. When he had finished, Barr
said, 'I'd love to know how much of this is

956
01:26:12,040 --> 01:26:13,040
true.'

957
01:26:13,040 --> 01:26:15,880
'So would we,' Coal said.

958
01:26:15,880 --> 01:26:19,260
'What did the President say about it?'

959
01:26:19,260 --> 01:26:25,380
'He agreed that the theory was implausible,
