960
01:26:25,380 --> 01:26:29,800
'Really? And what if it's true?'

961
01:26:29,800 --> 01:26:35,310
'Then the President has got problems. Me too.'

962
01:26:35,310 --> 01:26:42,130
They rode in silence for a while and watched
the traffic. Then Coal said, 'We need to know

963
01:26:42,130 --> 01:26:44,340
if the brief is true.'

964
01:26:44,340 --> 01:26:52,080
'If people are dying, it's true. Why else
did Callahan and Verheek die?'

965
01:26:52,080 --> 01:26:58,380
There was no other reason, and Coal knew it.
