966
01:26:58,380 --> 01:27:00,550
'Find the girl?'

967
01:27:00,550 --> 01:27:04,250
'No, go to Mattiece and talk to him.'

968
01:27:04,250 --> 01:27:09,000
'It won't be easy. He isn't exactly listed
in the phone book.'

969
01:27:09,000 --> 01:27:15,780
'You can do it. You've done more difficult
things for us in the past. You've done worse

970
01:27:15,780 --> 01:27:17,310
for us too.'

971
01:27:17,310 --> 01:27:22,230
'And you think Victor will trust me and tell
me his secrets?'

972
01:27:22,230 --> 01:27:29,150
'Why not? You're not a policeman. You can
help him; you can tell him that the press

973
01:27:29,150 --> 01:27:35,900
will have the story soon and so it would be
a good idea for him to disappear. Then he'll

974
01:27:35,900 --> 01:27:37,020
trust you.'

975
01:27:37,020 --> 01:27:41,220
'What if it's true? What will you do next?'

976
01:27:41,220 --> 01:27:46,949
'The first thing will be for the President
to appoint two nature-lovers to the Supreme

977
01:27:46,949 --> 01:27:54,070
Court; that will show people that we really
care for the environment. Then, at the same

978
01:27:54,070 --> 01:28:01,170
time, he will get the FBI to start an official
investigation into Victor Mattiece.'

979
01:28:01,170 --> 01:28:07,929
Barr was smiling with admiration. 'What about
the photograph?' he asked.

980
01:28:07,929 --> 01:28:15,330
'Easy. It's seven years old. We say that in
those days Mattiece was a good citizen, not

981
01:28:15,330 --> 01:28:22,810
a madman as he is now. Anyway, by Sunday I'll
tell you where he is. I've got a man working

982
01:28:22,810 --> 01:28:27,929
on it. Be ready to leave.'

983
01:28:27,929 --> 01:28:28,929
***

984
01:28:28,929 --> 01:28:34,520
Darby called Gray at 9:30 the next morning
