985
01:28:34,520 --> 01:28:39,370
'Where are you calling from?' Gray asked.

986
01:28:39,370 --> 01:28:44,570
'I'm staying at the Tabard Inn. I saw an old
friend in New York and decided it was time

987
01:28:44,570 --> 01:28:51,239
to leave. I hope I didn't bring any of them
with me. I bought two plane tickets with my

988
01:28:51,239 --> 01:28:57,640
card, for them to follow, but I paid cash
for the one I really used. Even then I changed

989
01:28:57,640 --> 01:29:05,290
planes four times. If they follow me here,
they must be magicians. If I see any of them

990
01:29:05,290 --> 01:29:07,640
here, I think I'll just surrender.'

991
01:29:07,640 --> 01:29:10,000
'When do we meet?'

992
01:29:10,000 --> 01:29:18,580
'Meet me in the restaurant here at nine tonight.
