993
01:29:18,580 --> 01:29:25,130
one. And be ready to stay away from your home
and office for a few days. I've booked you

994
01:29:25,130 --> 01:29:27,699
a room at the Marbury Hotel.'

995
01:29:27,699 --> 01:29:31,070
'Surely the office is safe, Darby.'

996
01:29:31,070 --> 01:29:37,360
'I'm not in the mood to argue. If you're going
to be difficult, Gray, I'll simply disappear.

997
01:29:37,360 --> 01:29:46,929
I'm sure I'll live longer out of the country,
anyway. I've got to go now. You be careful.'

998
01:29:46,929 --> 01:29:47,929
***

999
01:29:47,929 --> 01:29:52,190
The Marbury was close to where his boss, Smith
Keen, lived, and there were some things they

1000
01:29:52,190 --> 01:29:58,690
had to talk about. The next morning he rang
Keen from his room and they arranged to meet

1001
01:29:58,690 --> 01:30:05,080
outside the front of the hotel in fifteen
minutes. While they drove around in Keen's

1002
01:30:05,080 --> 01:30:11,650
car they discussed various ways in which they
