01:30:34,000 --> 01:30:40,179
near his hotel, he bought a sandwich and a
cup of coffee, and returned to his room. An

1008
01:30:40,179 --> 01:30:46,890
Asian cleaning woman was working outside his
room. 'Did you forget something, sir?' she

1009
01:30:46,890 --> 01:30:53,060
asked. Gray looked at her. 'What do you mean?'

1010
01:30:53,060 --> 01:30:55,760
'You just left your room, sir, and now you're
