1013
01:31:04,780 --> 01:31:10,570
closely. 'But now I see that it was another
man, sir.'

1014
01:31:10,570 --> 01:31:16,710
He walked quickly to the stairs and ran all
the way down to the ground floor. What was

1015
01:31:16,710 --> 01:31:25,100
in his room? Nothing important - just some
