1016
01:31:25,100 --> 01:31:28,420
at the Tabard Inn was in his pocket.

1017
01:31:28,420 --> 01:31:35,050
He had to find her, and quick.

1018
01:31:35,050 --> 01:31:40,739
CHAPTER FOURTEEN
Curtis D. Morgan

1019
01:31:40,739 --> 01:31:45,400
Darby spent the day in the Georgetown law
