1021
01:31:52,770 --> 01:31:54,050
wandered.

1022
01:31:54,050 --> 01:31:57,510
She thought a lot about Thomas.

1023
01:31:57,510 --> 01:31:58,510
***

1024
01:31:58,510 --> 01:32:02,719
Matthew Barr went to New Orleans, where he
