1030
01:32:27,690 --> 01:32:28,690
***

1031
01:32:28,690 --> 01:32:35,060
She stepped on the note when she opened her
door. It said: Darby, I'm in the garden. It's

1032
01:32:35,060 --> 01:32:44,179
urgent. Gray. She locked the door, went downstairs,
