1033
01:32:44,179 --> 01:32:49,120
She found him sitting at a small table, half
hidden behind a wall.

1034
01:32:49,120 --> 01:32:56,790
'Why are you here?' she demanded in a whisper.
He told her what had happened, and what he'd

1035
01:32:56,790 --> 01:33:02,510
done for the rest of the day. He had spent
