1036
01:33:02,510 --> 01:33:10,810
taxis, waiting for dark. Then he came to the
Tabard. He was certain that no one had followed

1037
01:33:10,810 --> 01:33:11,810
him.

1038
01:33:11,810 --> 01:33:16,940
She listened. She watched the restaurant and
